window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Holiday Greetings from Sugar and Booze </i>is a music-filled holiday comedy starring Ana Gasteyer and Maya Rudolph, with a jolly cast including Patti LuPone, Rachel Dratch, and Richard Kind. In this heartwarming story of love and friendship, we follow the journey of “Sugar” and “Booze” as they go from inseparable college buddies to busy working moms who mostly keep in touch with each other, and their close friends and family, through annual holiday letters. Pulled apart by distance and their hectic lives, their friendship nears a breaking point. That is until one December, when everything comes to a head at their annual holiday fete. Can their friendship survive the holidays?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Holiday Greetings from Sugar and Booze </i>features music from Ana Gasteyer’s album <b><i>sugar &amp; booze</i></b><i>, </i>available now at sugarandboozealbum.com.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
